      "name": "README.md",
      "filePath": "apps/print-agent/README.md",
      "summary": "Mesa 打印助手主文档，涵盖 print_jobs 拉取、LAN/USB 打印、config.json 配置、Windows 安装发布与本地 Docker 开发命令。",
      "tags": ["documentation", "print-agent", "deployment", "onboarding"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "document:apps/print-agent/RELEASE_NOTES.md",
      "type": "document",
      "name": "RELEASE_NOTES.md",
      "filePath": "apps/print-agent/RELEASE_NOTES.md",
      "summary": "打印助手版本发布说明，按 semver 记录小票排版、托盘菜单、配对向导等迭代变更，供 CI 发布流程读取。",
      "tags": ["documentation", "print-agent", "release-notes", "changelog"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:apps/print-agent/configure_ui.html",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "configure_ui.html",
      "filePath": "apps/print-agent/configure_ui.html",
      "summary": "已配对后的打印机配置向导页面，支持扫描 LAN/USB 打印机、映射 print station、保存映射与可选测试打印，含调试面板与 i18n。",
      "tags": ["component", "wizard", "print-agent", "i18n", "event-handler"],
      "complexity": "complex",
      "languageNotes": "内联 JavaScript 通过本地 HTTP API（/api/configure-state、/api/printers 等）与 Go agent 交互，依赖 MesaWizardUI 共享库。"
    },
    {
      "id": "config:apps/print-agent/go.mod",
      "type": "config",
      "name": "go.mod",
      "filePath": "apps/print-agent/go.mod",
      "summary": "Go 1.22 模块声明，定义 mesa-print-agent 依赖：WinSpool 打印、系统托盘 systray 及 golang.org/x 扩展库。",
      "tags": ["configuration", "go-module", "build-system", "print-agent"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "config:apps/print-agent/go.sum",
      "type": "config",
      "name": "go.sum",
      "filePath": "apps/print-agent/go.sum",
      "summary": "Go 模块依赖校验和锁定文件，与 go.mod 配套确保可重现构建。",
      "tags": ["configuration", "go-module", "build-system", "checksums"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:apps/print-agent/pair_ui.html",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "pair_ui.html",
      "filePath": "apps/print-agent/pair_ui.html",
      "summary": "首次配对向导页面，收集 Mesa API URL 与 6 位配对码，调用 /api/pair 完成设备绑定并引导进入配置页。",
      "tags": ["component", "wizard", "pairing", "print-agent", "i18n"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:apps/print-agent/setup_ui.html",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "setup_ui.html",
      "filePath": "apps/print-agent/setup_ui.html",
      "summary": "首次运行 setup 向导页面，扫描打印机、映射站点、保存配置并引导测试打印确认，完成后关闭向导窗口。",
      "tags": ["component", "wizard", "onboarding", "print-agent", "i18n"],
      "complexity": "complex",
      "languageNotes": "与 configure_ui 共享打印机列表合并逻辑，通过 MesaWizardUI 调用 /api/setup 系列端点。"
    },
    {
      "id": "function:apps/print-agent/configure_ui.html:loadPage",
      "type": "function",
      "name": "loadPage",
      "filePath": "apps/print-agent/configure_ui.html",
      "lineRange": [710, 756],
      "summary": "配置页主加载流程：拉取 agent 状态、应用 i18n、渲染配对门禁，已配对时加载云端站点并按需自动扫描打印机。",
      "tags": ["event-handler", "wizard", "bootstrap", "api-handler"],
      "complexity": "complex"
    },
    {
      "id": "function:apps/print-agent/configure_ui.html:runScan",
      "type": "function",
      "name": "runScan",
      "filePath": "apps/print-agent/configure_ui.html",
      "lineRange": [628, 681],
      "summary": "触发 /api/printers?refresh=1 扫描 LAN 与 WinSpool 打印机，合并已保存地址并刷新各站点下拉框，含并发去重与 stale 请求丢弃。",
      "tags": ["api-handler", "printer-discovery", "wizard"],
      "complexity": "complex"
    },
    {
      "id": "function:apps/print-agent/configure_ui.html:fillSelect",
      "type": "function",
      "name": "fillSelect",
      "filePath": "apps/print-agent/configure_ui.html",
      "lineRange": [423, 471],
      "summary": "重建单个站点打印机下拉框，按 LAN/Windows 分组展示扫描与已保存打印机，并为孤儿地址提供 fallback 选项。",
      "tags": ["utility", "dom", "wizard"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "function:apps/print-agent/configure_ui.html:renderStations",
      "type": "function",
      "name": "renderStations",
      "filePath": "apps/print-agent/configure_ui.html",
      "lineRange": [473, 505],
      "summary": "根据云端站点与本地已保存映射渲染站点行，每行含站点名称与打印机选择器，并同步刷新测试打印站点列表。",
      "tags": ["dom", "wizard", "render"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "function:apps/print-agent/configure_ui.html:rebuildPrinterLists",
      "type": "function",
      "name": "rebuildPrinterLists",
      "filePath": "apps/print-agent/configure_ui.html",
      "lineRange": [384, 421],
      "summary": "合并扫描结果与 config.json 中已保存的打印机地址，按 tcp/winspool 分组并记录 dedupe 统计供调试面板展示。",
      "tags": ["utility", "printer-discovery", "merge"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "function:apps/print-agent/setup_ui.html:loadSaved",
      "type": "function",
      "name": "loadSaved",
      "filePath": "apps/print-agent/setup_ui.html",
      "lineRange": [450, 484],
      "summary": "Setup 向导入口：读取 /api/setup-state 恢复已保存映射与 UI 语言偏好，然后启动打印机与站点 bootstrap。",
      "tags": ["bootstrap", "wizard", "api-handler"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "function:apps/print-agent/setup_ui.html:bootstrapPrinterSection",
      "type": "function",
      "name": "bootstrapPrinterSection",
      "filePath": "apps/print-agent/setup_ui.html",
      "lineRange": [418, 448],
      "summary": "并行拉取打印机列表与云端 print-stations，应用结果后渲染站点映射表格，处理扫描或站点加载失败提示。",
      "tags": ["bootstrap", "api-handler", "wizard"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "function:apps/print-agent/setup_ui.html:fillStationSelect",
      "type": "function",
      "name": "fillStationSelect",
      "filePath": "apps/print-agent/setup_ui.html",
      "lineRange": [295, 337],
      "summary": "为单个站点填充 LAN/Windows 分组打印机下拉选项，支持已保存但当前未扫描到的孤儿打印机地址。",
      "tags": ["utility", "dom", "wizard"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "function:apps/print-agent/setup_ui.html:renderStations",
      "type": "function",
      "name": "renderStations",
      "filePath": "apps/print-agent/setup_ui.html",
